此》(Cowboys Are Overly Secretly Fond Of Each Other) 封面的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥维尔·佩克和威利·纳尔逊。图片来源：Matt Winkelmeyer 和 Terry Wyatt，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/orville-peck">奥维尔·派克 (Orville Peck)</a>与乡村传奇人物<a href="/artists/willie-nelson">威利·尼尔森 (Willie Nelson)</a>合作翻唱了内德·萨莱特 (Ned Sublette) 的《牛仔们经常秘密地喜欢彼此》(Cowboys AreFrequently Secretly Fond Of Each Other)。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orvile-peck-bronco-review-3195236">奥维尔·佩克（Orville Peck）——《野马》评论：蒙面男子以复古乡村的炫目裸露他的灵魂</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲是佩克与华纳唱片公司签约后的首张专辑。 《Cowboys AreFrequently Secretly Fond Of Each Other》由 Sublette 于 1981 年录制，并于 2006 年由 Nelson 翻唱。</p><p>佩克在谈到<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-country/orville-peck-willie-nelson-dropcowboys-are-frequently-secretly-fond-each-other-1234999336/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石</em></a>乐队时说：“威利一直在谈论这首歌中的主题比以往任何时候都重要。他希望它与我们两个人一起生活。”</p><p>他继续说：“如今，围绕着LGBTQIA+社区的所有言论，拥有像威利这样的真正的盟友，不怕自豪地站在我们旁边真是令人鼓舞。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="奥维尔·佩克和威利·纳尔逊 - 牛仔们常常暗自喜欢对方（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BirJMnMcfBs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>由本·普林斯（Ben Prince）执导的二重奏伴随的视频具有酷儿男女跳舞的片段，并在轿车里喝酒。佩克和纳尔逊在尼尔森运气牧场的一棵树下唱歌和弹吉他。</p><p>这首歌是第一个从蒙面歌手即将发行的二重奏专辑“ Stampede”中发行的曲目。佩克（Peck）访问Instagram分享了即将推出的LP的消息，“&#39;Stampede&#39;My Duets专辑，其中有我的几个好朋友来了。”</p><p> “ Stampede”将跟随2022年的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orvile-peck-bronco-review-3195236">Bronco</a> ”。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orvile-peck-bronco-review-3195236">专辑的四星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享了：“这是一个丰富的风景：完全现代而自豪的酷儿。这是一张毫不掩饰的成长的专辑，因为艺术家的感受，但永远不会陷入自怜。蒙面的牛仔在矛盾的是 - 露出了他的灵魂，无限制，而且对此一切都更好。在“野马”上，佩克（Peck）与专辑的复古乡村狂欢舞蹈（Razzle-Dazzle）一样，扮演着自己的身份。让他骑着马扫到尘土飞扬的日落中。”</p><p>佩克还宣布了他的2024年北美“踩踏”之旅。请查看以下日期的完整列表，然后<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Forville-peck-tickets%2Fartist%2F2532151" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5WHix_x0T7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-rig